<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Offener Brief des Rates</head><p>Der Rat bevollmächtigt Konrad Pilsacher und Hans Stetzmann, Diener der Stadt, zur Vertretung in der Klage des Landrichters Hans Lotterbeck vor dem Landgericht zu Hirschberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_94" id="47r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l18">VVir ~ dy <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des
                <expan>R<ex>ats</ex></expan> etc <expan>Bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc vmb ſölch klag
            vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l19"><expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> / Als Hans loterbeck /
            lantrichter / getan hat <add><ab facs="#facs_94_line_1576677194181_4777">vnd tut
              </ab></add> /auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l20"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> gute in der <expan>lantſchranne<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l21"><expan>hirſſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> gelegen / daʒ vvir darümb
                <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> pilſacher vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l22">Hanſen Stecʒman <expan>vnſre<ex>n</ex></expan> diener /
                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_line_1576677212078_4797"><expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd
                <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gevvalt vnd macht / vns vnd
              <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l28">gute <add><ab facs="#facs_94_line_1576677227679_4815">gen Jm
              </ab></add> cʒu <expan>verantvvurtte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd cʒu
              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>treten</expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l29">vnd an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat cʒugevvynn vnd
            cʒuverluſt vnd cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l30">allem rechten / Mit <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicʒ
                <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_94" id="47r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, dy <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des <expan>r<ex>ats</ex></expan> etc.,
                <expan>bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc. umb sölch klag und
              <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> als Hans Loterbeck, lantrichter, getan hat <add>und
              tut</add> auf <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> gute in der <expan>lantschranne<ex>n</ex></expan> czu
                <expan>Hirssp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> gelegen, daz wir darümb
              <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Pilsacher und Hansen Steczman,
              <expan>unsre<ex>n</ex></expan> diener, <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gancze<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt und macht, uns
            und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> gute <add>gen im</add> czu
              <expan>verantwurtte<ex>n</ex></expan> und czu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>treten</expan> von
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen und an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat czu
            gewynn und czu verlust und czu allem rechten. Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicz
                <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
